ikasi otomatis yang dikirimkan TriPay ke server Mitra saat status transaksi berubah (terutama saat pembayaran berhasil). Halaman ini menjelaskan cara kerja, konfigurasi, dan penanganan callback.",[220,221],"hr",{},[223,224,226],"h2",{"id":225},"pengertian-callbackipn","Pengertian Callback/IPN",[208,228,229,231,232,235],{},[211,230,217],{}," adalah HTTP request yang dikirimkan oleh server TriPay ke URL yang ditentukan oleh Mitra untuk memberitahukan perubahan status transaksi secara ",[211,233,234],{},"real-time",".",[237,238,240],"h3",{"id":239},"fungsi-callback","Fungsi Callback",[242,243,245],"list",{"type":244},"info",[246,247,248,256,263,272],"ul",{},[249,250,251,252,255],"li",{},"Memberitahu Mitra bahwa pembayaran telah ",[211,253,254],{},"berhasil"," (PAID)",[249,257,258,259,262],{},"Memungkinkan Mitra untuk ",[211,260,261],{},"update status pesanan"," secara otomatis",[249,264,265,266,268,269],{},"Mendukung proses bisnis yang ",[211,267,234],{}," dan ",[211,270,271],{},"otomatis",[249,273,274],{},"Mengurangi kebutuhan pengecekan manual",[220,276],{},[223,278,280],{"id":279},"cara-kerja-callback","Cara Kerja Callback",[237,282,284],{"id":283},"alur-proses","Alur Proses",[286,287,292],"pre",{"className":288,"code":290,"language":291},[289],"language-text","1. Pelanggan Melakukan Pembayaran\n              ↓\n2. Pembayaran Diverifikasi oleh PJP Rekanan\n              ↓\n3. Status Transaksi Berubah ke PAID di Sistem TriPay\n              ↓\n4. TriPay Mengirim HTTP POST ke Callback URL Mitra\n              ↓\n5. Server Mitra Menerima dan Memproses Data\n              ↓\n6. Server Mitra Mengembalikan Response (JSON)\n              ↓\n7. Mitra Update Status Pesanan di Sistem Internal\n","text",[293,294,290],"code",{"__ignoreMap":295},"",[237,297,299],{"id":298},"kapan-callback-dikirim","Kapan Callback Dikirim?",[301,302,303,316],"table",{},[304,305,306],"thead",{},[307,308,309,313],"tr",{},[310,311,312],"th",{},"Event",[310,314,315],{},"Callback Dikirim",[317,318,319